{"tid":1387763,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對於區議會 我有野想講","createTime":"2019-07-30T15:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T19:29:31.000Z","uid":161000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"05598b194c453bdc77721e608351405c9d828dc6","tid":1387763,"uid":161000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:04:05.000Z","msg":"2019年香港區議會選舉會係11月24日舉行<br />\n呢個選舉係6/9 6/12 6/16... 之後嘅第一次選舉 非常重要!!!<br />\n建制派之所以次次都好多票 而且係因為佢地識得配票<br />\n依家我地有成200萬人肯上街嘅時候<br />\n點解唔學建制派咁 係票站門口做問卷 再好好運用選票<br />\n而唔係好似上次立法會咁一窩蜂投朱凱廸 (以84,121票成為香港地區直選的票王)<br />\n唔單止我地要list哂有邊D候選人係自己人 (公報左候選人之後) 再宣傳出去<br />\n我地仲要組織義工團 助選同配票<br />\n咁先至減少到建制派係地區上嘅蛇齋餅粽"},{"pid":"50705f213c39c1cce141ccf3afd919193bcaaad0","tid":1387763,"uid":161000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:14:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b035d897a11f6e02f1abaa300ab1f48630afc6bb","tid":1387763,"uid":161000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:14:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02c0ff75288eb5633099557f30ff7f2cf64f35af","tid":1387763,"uid":161000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:19:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"980b41d6b29ec0526a086501e74c923205f50b94","tid":1387763,"uid":161000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:19:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36974a81f4f7d25e83e59655508bbec0f0d24cf7","tid":1387763,"uid":135169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:20:43.000Z","msg":"區議會可以點配票⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6abb08b9727627a52c19abf9ea4230d02d1b6589","tid":1387763,"uid":263991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:21:32.000Z","msg":"單議席單票制需要配票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"643cd48e0f101bad43cb8c42ef1c1c11b66f1ca1","tid":1387763,"uid":245644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T19:22:08.000Z","msg":"其實係咪